      <title>习近平称中国“永远不会忘记”美国轰炸其大使馆的事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/xi-vows-to-remember-flagrant-us-bombing-of-chinese-embassy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[习近平主席誓言“永远不会忘记”北约对中国驻贝尔格莱德大使馆的致命轰炸，数小时后他将穿越欧洲抵达塞尔维亚，旨在分裂布鲁塞尔对美国的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/xi-vows-to-remember-flagrant-us-bombing-of-chinese-embassy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 06:57:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
